<br>
A bunch of people got hit by a really nasty disease slow - someone had given me AQ for haste but I was still swinging through molasass. Something was also casting a curse on people that reduced all of your stats to 1. Lots of mounts got summoned at that point just so we could move. I was running around loaning my bridle to my poor encumbrance-rooted guildmates.<br>
<br>
At the end the GMs awarded the grand prize (a gnome illusion mask) to Synth, a bard who'd kept shouting amusing encouraging rhymes through the whole thing (and had died at least once). The monsters also dropped a bunch of fairly nice stuff, Phase Spider Carapace was the big one I remember, and a Sebilisian Berserker Cloak, and a bunch of other stuff, and everyone was very friendly and well-behaved and rolled /randoms at the end to hand it out. Special props to Warz of Resolution who kicked the most butt and organized the rolling at the end.<br>
<br>
Also thanks to the healers who stuck around afterward and cured everyone's diseases and curses. Telorea and Gravely  were the ones who healed me and my guildmates but I know there were others too.<br>
<br>
And of course, thanks for getting your butts off Imperial land before we had to lay the smack down on all of you for trespassing after the dragon was dead. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
This server is great. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=krostgutshank>Krost Gutshank</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 9<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/27/03 4:50 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4960.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: GM event in LOIO tonight</span><hr size=1> Yeah, it really was enjoyable despite the fact that I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>still</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> refuse to learn the languages of the softskins and the only reason I knew what the hell was being said was Voskor's occasional words in channel. I had a blast.<br>
